message.body: Hey Lisa, I left a voicemail a few days ago but never heard back, let me know when another convenient time to call would be if you're still interested in me working for you. Thanks!
Yes. Sorry about the delay in getting back to you. It's been crazy with end of the school year activities.
Totally understandable! Just wanted to make sure my message didn't get lost in the mix. :)
You can call me tomorrow or we can just plan a time this week if you want to go ahead and jump back in!
Yeah, just starting this week would be fine! My daytime hours are all free (being out of school is great!) so whatever works best for you is fine for me.
Tuesday at 10 for a few hours?
